          Aircraft Laser Infrared Absorption Spectrometer (ALIAS):
   a QC Laser Spectrometer for H[2]O, HDO, H[2]^17O, H[2]^18O, CO, CH[4],
               & ^13CO[2]/CO[2] on NASA's CRYSTAL-FACE Mission
               Christopher R. Webster(PI), Gregory J. Flesch,
        Katy Modarress, Jesse Landeros, Ron Howe, W. Steven Woodward

     Previous contributors:  Robert Herman, David C. Scott, James E.
     Swanson, Randy D. May, Curtis A. Trimble, Robert G. Chave, Matthew
     A. Tuchscherer, James Kendall, Dr. Lyatt Jaegle, Dr. Hua Hu, Gwen
     Eknayan, Julie Jensen, Ronald Howe, George Mohler, Ted Brunzie,
     Alissa Fitzgerald, Scott Atkinson

